All right.

133
00:10:18,920 --> 00:10:21,399
You know very well what kind of a person he is.

134
00:10:21,400 --> 00:10:24,340
He is a stiff man who doesn't know how to have fun.

135
00:10:24,340 --> 00:10:26,320
Moreover, he has won so many awards.

136
