Sorry.

156
00:12:19,160 --> 00:12:20,660
What is it?

157
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:23,000
What?

158
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:27,800
You've won the Jin An Award.

159
00:12:28,480 --> 00:12:30,560
What is your next plan?

160
00:12:31,600 --> 00:12:34,320
After winning the Jin An Award,

161
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:38,340
I will continue my plan.

162
00:12:42,700 --> 00:12:46,159
Chuan, do you know this adage?

163
00:12:46,160 --> 00:12:49,380
Plans always fall behind changes.

164
00:12:49,380 --> 00:12:50,920
What changes?

165
00:12:52,760 --> 00:12:58,400
Over the years, I noticed that you've been changing.

166
00:12:59,320 --> 00:13:04,279
So as your dearest brother and as a friend who loves you

167
00:13:04,280 --> 00:13:05,860
and you love the most,

168
00:13:05,860 --> 00:13:11,480
I must remind you that it's time to change your unreliable plan.

169
00:13:12,800 --> 00:13:15,560
Even if I changed the plan,

170
00:13:15,560 --> 00:13:18,120
the outcome would stay the same.

171
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:20,500
It's going to happen sooner or later.

172
00:13:24,840 --> 00:13:28,540
The more time you have, the better your chance is.

173
00:13:28,540 --> 00:13:32,140
Moreover, even if you don't care about yourself,

174
00:13:32,140 --> 00:13:35,180
at least be considerate of those around you.

175
00:13:35,180 --> 00:13:39,880
Are you going to leave me and your parents behind?

176
00:13:39,880 --> 00:13:43,439
Or are you going to leave the Chuan Studio and those

177
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:45,480
who fought by your side behind?

178
00:13:46,640 --> 00:13:48,980
What about Jiang Xiaoning?

179
00:13:48,980 --> 00:13:50,620
She is still young.

180
00:13:50,620 --> 00:13:53,760
She has neither a degree nor a family of her own.

181
00:13:53,760 --> 00:13:55,879
You act like a father figure all the time.

182
00:13:55,880 --> 00:13:58,840
Are you going to leave her and let her go?

183
00:14:06,360 --> 00:14:08,240
Just think about it.

184
00:14:33,160 --> 00:14:34,279
Why are you still here?

185
00:14:34,280 --> 00:14:35,879
I was waiting to drive you home.

186
00:14:35,880 --> 00:14:37,460
Don't bother. I'm busy.

187
00:14:37,460 --> 00:14:39,280
Let me drive you there.

188
00:14:50,360 --> 00:14:54,320
Boss, are you feeling unhappy because you've won enough awards?

189
00:14:54,320 --> 00:14:57,159
Or is there something else that is even more upsetting?

190
00:14:57,160 --> 00:14:59,620
You've been pulling on a long face the whole day.

191
00:15:00,180 --> 00:15:01,620
Have I?

192
00:15:01,620 --> 00:15:03,220
You should look at yourself in the mirror.

193
00:15:03,220 --> 00:15:05,460
You're wearing a worried frown.

194
00:15:09,760 --> 00:15:11,599
Boss, are you sure you don't need a ride?

195
00:15:11,600 --> 00:15:13,640
Yes, I've called a taxi. You should go home.

196
00:15:13,640 --> 00:15:15,060
What about tomorrow morning?

197
00:15:15,060 --> 00:15:17,059
- Wait for my notice. 
 - Okay.

198
00:15:29,500 --> 00:15:32,650
Boss, I don't know why you're upset,

199
00:15:32,650 --> 00:15:36,720
but I must tell you this. Congratulations.

200
00:15:36,720 --> 00:15:41,759
No matter what happened, achieving a dream is never a bad thing. Right?

201
00:15:43,120 --> 00:15:46,360
What if achieving a dream is a bad thing?

202
00:15:46,360 --> 00:15:49,260
Why would it be a bad thing?

203
00:15:50,180 --> 00:15:52,480
Because you would no longer have a goal.

204
00:15:53,920 --> 00:15:55,119
That's simple.

205
00:15:55,120 --> 00:15:57,520
Just set another goal for yourself.

206
00:15:57,520 --> 00:16:00,700
Take me for an example. My dream is to go skiing.

207
00:16:00,700 --> 00:16:02,999
And my dream has come true.

208
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:06,620
I also want to graduate and get my certificate.

209
00:16:06,620 --> 00:16:11,300
I also want to become an outstanding architectural designer like you.

210
00:16:13,920 --> 00:16:18,799
Boss, when it concerns a dream, you can go with a greater goal.

211
00:16:21,040 --> 00:16:23,600
If it takes you some time to figure it out,

212
00:16:23,600 --> 00:16:27,440
I wouldn't mind spending some of my time and energy to provide you

213
00:16:27,440 --> 00:16:30,960
with some reasonable advice for your reference.

214
00:16:30,960 --> 00:16:32,439
I look forward to your advice.

215
00:16:32,440 --> 00:16:34,220
Sure.

216
00:16:36,360 --> 00:16:38,359
No problem, Boss. I'll keep it in mind.

217
00:16:38,359 --> 00:16:40,999
Sir, I'll leave him to you. Drive safely.

218
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:42,380
Boss, see you tomorrow.

219
00:16:42,380 --> 00:16:44,520
Stay safe.

220
00:17:04,620 --> 00:17:06,639
  Son, shouldn't you be in bed now? 

221
00:17:06,639 --> 00:17:09,180
I couldn't sleep.

222
00:17:09,180 --> 00:17:13,000
 What could be so exciting that it keeps my son awake at night? 

223
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:15,539
I've won an award. I've won the Jin An Award.

224
00:17:15,560 --> 00:17:17,400
 Really? 

225
00:17:17,400 --> 00:17:20,139
Gu! Come here!  Your son has won an award!

226
00:17:20,139 --> 00:17:21,679
- What is it? 
 - Hurry!

227
00:17:21,679 --> 00:17:22,820
What did he win this time?

228
00:17:22,820 --> 00:17:25,080
 The Jin An Award. 

229
00:17:31,120 --> 00:17:32,620
Really?

230
00:17:33,380 --> 00:17:36,259
If he had won such a prestigious award, wouldn't he put a smile on his face?

231
00:17:36,259 --> 00:17:38,000
 Are you sure? 

232
00:17:38,000 --> 00:17:39,320
 Don't be silly. 

233
00:17:39,320 --> 00:17:42,439
When did he ever lie to us with such a serious matter?

234
00:17:42,440 --> 00:17:44,559
Then he just doesn't want to see me.

235
00:17:44,560 --> 00:17:46,020
You two carry on.

236
00:17:46,020 --> 00:17:47,700
Father.

237
00:17:47,700 --> 00:17:48,839
Come here.

238
00:17:48,840 --> 00:17:50,400
He asked for you.

239
00:17:51,440 --> 00:17:54,120
 Father, I am telling you this great news 

240
00:17:54,120 --> 00:17:56,840
 because I'm very happy. 

241
00:17:56,840 --> 00:18:00,880
 I just found it hard to smile for the camera. 

242
00:18:03,120 --> 00:18:05,180
Then don't smile.

243
00:18:05,180 --> 00:18:08,460
I remember when you went on stage for the awards when you were little,

244
00:18:08,460 --> 00:18:10,519
I never saw you smile either.

245
00:18:10,520 --> 00:18:12,659
Are you serious? It's different.

246
00:18:12,659 --> 00:18:15,079
It's an international award!

247
00:18:15,080 --> 00:18:17,080
 Gu, what's got into you? 

248
00:18:17,280 --> 00:18:18,159
 Xiao Chuan, 

249
00:18:18,160 --> 00:18:20,919
 you don't need all the success and glory. 

250
00:18:20,920 --> 00:18:22,119
 Don't be so tense all the time. It's bad for your mental health. 

251
00:18:25,120 --> 00:18:27,999
 Not to mention you've won so many awards at a young age. 

252
00:18:28,000 --> 00:18:30,039
 Your career is taking off. 

253
00:18:30,040 --> 00:18:31,720
 You should be content. 

254
00:18:32,320 --> 00:18:34,000
I am.

255
00:18:35,680 --> 00:18:38,219
Father. Mother.

256
00:18:39,280 --> 00:18:41,740
You must be very disappointed in me.

257
00:18:41,740 --> 00:18:42,980
Nonsense.

258
00:18:42,980 --> 00:18:47,060
As your parents, we are both very proud of you.

259
00:18:47,060 --> 00:18:51,800
 After so many years, I never listened to your advice. 

260
00:18:51,800 --> 00:18:54,860
 I didn't get married or become a father. 

261
00:18:54,860 --> 00:18:57,700
